ts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mere%20fact%20of%20belonging%20to%20the%20majority%20community%20instills%20them%20with%20the%20belief%20that%20they%20rule%20the%20realm%20as%20much%20as%20those%20who%20actually%20wield%20state%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20days%20ago%2C%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%2C%20a%20poor%20person%20(fortuitously%20a%20Muslim%20named%20Isar%20Mohammed%3F)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-mob-lynched-muslim-prasad-banana-theft-ganesh-ganapati%5C%22%3Ewas%20caught%20allegedly%20stealing%20%3Cem%3Eprasad%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(offering%20to%20the%20deity)%2C%20tied%20to%20a%20pole%2C%20and%20mercilessly%20lynched%20for%20some%20five%20hours%20till%20he%20died.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20while%2C%20ostensibly%2C%20the%20deity%20looked%20on%20and%20did%20not%20take%20his%20part.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20popular%20Hindu%20theological%20culture%2C%20there%20is%20a%20resonant%20adage%3A%20%3Cem%3Ekhali%20paet%20bhajan%20na%20hovei%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Gopala.%20Translated%2C%20it%20means%2C%20%E2%80%98sorry%2C%20lord%2C%20cannot%20pray%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20truism%20seems%20now%20to%20have%20found%20its%20authoritarian%20reversal%3A%20those%20that%20have%20shall%20get%2C%20those%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20shall%20die%20for%20wanting%20to%20get.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20that%20time%20when%20religious%20practices%20were%20validated%20by%20their%20human%20content%3A%20they%20were%20either%20caring%20or%20uncaring%20of%20concrete%20misery%20among%20living%20beings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20any%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGods%20and%20corresponding%20governments%20now%20follow%20the%20Calvinist%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%9Celection%E2%80%9D%3A%20you%20are%20either%20in%20grace%20with%20the%20gods%2C%20or%20you%20are%20not%3B%20and%20in%20either%20case%2C%20the%20matter%20is%20not%20subject%20to%20reasoned%20iteration%20in%20pursuit%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20only%20the%20propertied%20can%20be%20in%20a%20state%20of%20grace%2C%20their%20earthly%20status%20being%20proof%20that%20god%20loves%20them%2C%20and%20will%20do%20so%20hereafter%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20forget%20about%20what%20Allah%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20said%20to%20the%20Mullah%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20was%20presented%20before%20him%20upon%20earthly%20demise%3A%20%E2%80%98Send%20this%20man%20to%20%3Cem%3Ejahanum%3C%2Fem%3E%20(hell)%2C%E2%80%99%20He%20is%20heard%20to%20have%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20astonished%20priest%20complained%20that%20all%20his%20life%20he%20never%20missed%20namaz%2C%20roza%2C%20Haj%2C%20giving%20zakat%20(charity)%2C%20etc.%2C%20Allah%20retorted%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20did%20you%20do%20when%20I%20visited%20you%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYa%20Allah%2C%20when%20did%20you%20do%20so%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20did%20you%20treat%20the%20orphan%20boy%20who%20came%20to%20your%20door%20for%20a%20morsel%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20so-self-righteous%20Mullah%E2%80%99s%20face%20fell.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20now%2C%20go%20to%20jahanum%2C%20and%20none%20of%20your%20ritual%20allegiance%20to%20religion%20may%20save%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20quite%20sure%20Lord%20Ganesh%20%E2%80%93%20the%20deity%20in%20the%20pandal%20where%20the%20wretched%20hungry%20man%20was%20clubbed%20to%20death%20for%20stealing%20prasad%20%E2%80%93%20will%20say%20something%20similar%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98bhakts%E2%80%99%20when%20they%20appear%20for%20judgment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%20universe%20has%20no%20hell%20but%20they%20will%20surely%20receive%20their%20comeuppance%20in%20their%20rebirth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaybe%20they%20will%20be%20reborn%20as%20hungry%20sans-culottes%2C%20attempting%20to%20steal%20Prasad%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20will%20watch%2C%20along%20with%20Lord%20Ganesh%2C%20while%20the%20government%20marches%20along%20on%20its%20course%20of%20sanctifying%20development%20with%20muscular%20dharmic%20fanfare%20to%20drive%20home%20the%20point%20that%20Bharat%20is%20%3Cem%3Emahan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Vishwa%20guru.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBadri%20Raina%20taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696406445000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04131452%2FScreenshot-2023-10-04-at-1.12.51-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fganesh-prasad-muslim-man-lynching-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lord%20Ganesh%20%E2%80%93%20the%20deity%20in%20the%20pandal%20where%20the%20wretched%20hungry%20man%20was%20clubbed%20to%20death%20for%20allegedly%20stealing%20prasad%20%E2%80%93%20will%20have%20something%20to%20say%20to%20'bhakts'%20when%20they%20appear%20for%20judgment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fganesh-prasad-muslim-man-lynching-delhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2223%20Army%20Jawans%20Missing%20After%20Sikkim%20Flash%20Flood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04132527%2FF7kYy-qbQAA0XtK.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20flash%20flood%20in%20Sikkim%20has%20led%20to%2023%20Indian%20Army%20jawans%20being%20reported%20missing%20on%20Wednesday%20(October%204)%20morning.%20Reports%20say%20the%20flood%20was%20tri