%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-lok-sabha-hate-speech%5C%22%3Efilthy%20words%20spoken%20with%20vehemence%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%95%20and%20evident%20premeditation%2C%20considering%20the%20ease%20with%20which%20they%20flowed%20over%20a%20small%20interval%20in%20a%20pause%2C%20resume%2C%20pause%2C%20pattern%20rather%20than%20in%20the%20spontaneous%20outburst%20of%20a%20diseased%20mind%20%E2%80%95%20by%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20South%20Delhi%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20against%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20Amroha%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20sharpens%20India%E2%80%99s%20fundamental%20ideological%20contradiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20level%20of%20politics%2C%20this%20contradiction%20is%20exemplified%20by%20the%20struggle%20being%20waged%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20all%20that%20he%20has%20stood%20for%20%E2%80%95%20including%20a%20meticulously%20directed%20anti-Muslim%20pogrom%20on%20his%20watch%20%E2%80%95%20and%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20ongoing%20lynching%20of%20Muslims%20and%20the%20bulldozing%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20businesses%2C%20the%20frequent%20killing%20of%20Dalits%2C%20and%20the%20burning%20of%20churches%20on%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20watch%2C%20has%20taken%20on%20such%20meaning%20that%20his%20devotees%20feel%20empowered%20enough%20to%20take%20the%20law%20into%20their%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20operate%20through%C2%A0%3Cem%3Etanzeems%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0or%20organised%20cells%20and%20murderous%20gangs%20of%20the%20type%20seen%20in%20the%20late%20%E2%80%9980s%20and%20early%20%E2%80%9990s%20in%20Kashmir%20when%20Pakistan%2C%20just%20across%20the%20border%2C%20attempted%20to%20create%20a%20putsch%20through%20the%20%E2%80%98creative%E2%80%99%20use%20of%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20Pakistani%20involvement%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Etanzeems%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0are%20of%20a%20wholly%20different%20religious%20colour%2C%20and%20their%20support%20comes%20from%20official%20and%20police%20indifference%20or%20complicity.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20there%20are%20few%20instances%20of%20anyone%20being%20brought%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBidhuri%E2%80%99s%20flow%20of%20uncontaminated%20dirt%20has%20no%20parallel%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Parliament.%20It%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20mayhem%20that%20uncivil%20elements%20of%20civil%20society%20have%20been%20wreaking%20on%20the%20populace.%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20lingo%20is%20their%20street%20lingo.%20Its%20intention%20is%20to%20demonise%20and%20lynch%20or%20attack%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ramesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20Controversial%20Appointment%20Shows%20Hate%20Is%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Currency%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuris-controversial-appointment-shows-hate-is-bjps-political-currency%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20Controversial%20Appointment%20Shows%20Hate%20Is%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Currency%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20five-day%20Special%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20was%20to%20have%20featured%20sober%20reflection%20on%20its%2075%20years%2C%20starting%20from%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20But%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20own%20speech%20was%20vacuous%2C%20indicating%20a%20small%20mind%20at%20work%20behind%20high-sounding%20exclamations%20on%20a%20manufactured%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20been%20no%20advance%20planning.%20For%20a%20contrast%2C%20recall%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20GST%20regime%20in%20the%20Central%20Hall%20of%20Parliament%20at%20the%20stroke%20of%20the%20midnight%20hour%2C%20in%20a%20sordid%20mimicry%20of%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20at%20midnight%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20whole%20thing%20was%20a%20put-up%20job.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20did%20not%20even%20make%20a%20pretence%20of%20capturing%20the%20spirit%20and%20philosophy%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20show%20appreciation%20of%20what%20has%20been%20gained%20through%20Parliament%20in%20the%20seven%20decades%20of%20life%20after%20colonial%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBidhuri%20was%20the%20show-stealer.%20He%20was%20anything%20but%20vacuous.%20The%20video%20of%20his%20dark%20intervention%20in%20a%20discussion%20to%20congratulate%20our%20scientists%20for%20Chandrayan-3%2C%20has%20gone%20around%20the%20world%20much%20faster%20than%20Chandrayan%20itself%2C%20earning%20him%20unprecedented%20news%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20playbook%20of%20the%20ideological%C2%A0%3Cem%3Epaathshala%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0the%20MP%20has%20attended.%20Modi%2C%20many%20ministers%20and%20prominent%20BJP%20MPs%20derive%20their%20foundational%20nourishment%20from%20the%20same%20fellowship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%20what%20has%20transpired%2C%20the%20special%20session%2C%20sprung%20on%20the%20people%20like%20a%20clever%20election%20trick%2C%20can%20be%20said%20to%20have%20had%20dubious%20intent.%20It%20attained%20two%20fraudulent%20ends.%20The%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20pre-election%20season%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20female%20vote%2C%20but%20with%20a%20catch.%20It%20likely%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%20into%20effect%20for%20at%20least%20a%20decade%20if%20the%20BJP-RSS%20remain%20in%20the%20driver%E2%80%99s%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20was%20the%20Bidhuri%20effect%3A%20the%20%E2%80%9Csickular%20libtards%E2%80%9D%20were%20left%20foaming%20at%20the%20mouth%2C%20and%20the%20faithful%20overjoyed.%20Already%2C%20too%20many%20followers%20are%20drifting%20away%20following%20the%20return%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20elections%20are%20practically%20upon%20us%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20start%20mobilising%20on%20the%20single%20agenda%20which%20makes%20the%20saffron%20brigades%20and%20their%20brigadiers%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20less%20interesting%20is%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20episode.%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20has%20had%20it%20scrubbed%20from%20the%20record%2C%20using%20his%20power%20to%20expunge%20%E2%80%9Cunparliamentary%E2%80%9D%20remarks.%20Another%20blunt%20instrument%20BJP%20MP%20has%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20in%20fact%20Danish%20Ali%20who%20had%20invited%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20wrath%2C%20and%20called%20for%20an%20enquiry.%20Probably%2C%20this%20is%20what%20Shakespeare%20meant%20when%20he%20said%20the%20devil%20can%20quote%20scripture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20shortly%20after%20Bidhuri%20had%20left%20the%20House%20stunned%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20evidently%20the%20gentleman%20among%20the%20Hindutvawadi%20charioteers%20and%20not%20a%20hate-filled%20street%20fighter%20like%20his%20colleagues%2C%20rose%20to%20offer%20his%20regret%20%E2%80%9Cif%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20sentiment%20was%20hurt%E2%80%9D!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlas%2C%20he%20was%20not%20being%20true%20to%20his%20home%20turf%20of%20UP.%20Lucknow%2C%20over%20which%20Singh%20once%20presided%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20is%20justly%20known%20for%20its%20culture%20and%20refinement.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20conditional%2C%20lifeless%20apology%2C%20a%20joke%20to%20be%20dismissed%20with%20a%20wave%20of%20the%20hand%2C%20betrays%20other%20origins%20of%20his%20political%20make-up.%20Raksha%20Mantri%2C%20sorry%2C%20you%20goofed%20up%20real%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20truth%2C%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20onslaught%20was%20on%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20on%20which%20MPs%20take%20their%20oath%20and%2C%20more%20particularly%2C%20on%20its%20Basic%20Structure%2C%20which%20upholds%20secularism%20as%20a%20profound%20value%20on%20which%20rests%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20integrity%2C%20unity%20and%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20less%20pitiable%20than%20the%20torrent%20of%20abuse%20issuing%20from%20Bidhuri%20was%20the%20sight%20of%20two%20former%20high%20profile%20cabinet%20ministers%20of%20Modi%20%E2%80%95%20one%20a%20prominent%20BJP%20leader%20from%20Bihar%20and%20the%20other%20from%20Delhi%20%E2%80%95%20laughing%20uncontrollably%20as%20their%20unstoppable%20colleague%20did%20the%20hatchet%20job%20on%20Muslims%20to%20the%20fullest%20satisfaction%20of%20his%20ideological%20mates%20and%20mentors.%20In%20those%20dark%20words%20that%20pierce%20through%20the%20heart%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity%2C%20these%20seasoned%20political%20warriors%20found%20much%20humour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20on%20another%20day%2C%20another%20BJP%20MP%2C%20Pragya%20Thakur%2C%20had%20unleashed%20vitriol%20against%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20PM%20at%20least%20shed%20crocodile%20tears.%20He%20said%20in%20Parliament%20that%20he%20could%20never%20%E2%80%9Cforgive%E2%80%9D%20her.%20But%20just%20days%20after%20the%20discussion%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%2075%20years%20of%20our%20Parliament%2C%20the%20PM%20has%20chosen%20silence%20over%20words%20after%20the%20public%20traducing%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20hence%20of%20Parliament%20itself%2C%20by%20one%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9Cfirebrand%E2%80%9D%20MPs.%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20is%20transitioning%20through%20interesting%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20elections%20approach%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guidance%20is%20leaning%20forward%20to%20sharpen%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20primary%20ideological%20contradiction%20%E2%80%95%20which%20is%20that%20of%20a%20communal%20India%20heading%20toward%20establishing%20full%20sway%20for%20majority%20community%20supremacist%20thought%20as%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20harmonious%20India%20for%20all%20that%20we%20have%20nursed%20since%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20tawdry%20Bidhuri%20episode%2C%20other%20flashpoints%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20manufactured%2C%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20vote.%20The%20name%20of%20the%20game%20is%20polarisation.%20How%20will%20the%20Congress%20respond%3F%20Its%20ideological%20spine%20has%20lately%20been%20stiffened%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20after%20a%20long%20spell%20of%20the%20party%20not%20knowing%20what%20it%20stands%20for%2C%20but%20mouthing%20platitudes%20nevertheless.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%2C%20now%20running%20on%20his%20second%20wind%2C%20visited%20Danish%20Ali%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20an%20act%20of%20substance%20and%20symbolism.%20How%20will%20other%20INDIA%20constituents%20respond%3F%20Ideology%20is%20very%20important%2C%20but%20its%20vehicle%20is%20politics.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20national%20elections%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20if%20it%20is%20to%20offer%20a%20meaningful%20challenge%20to%20the%20ruling%20clique%2C%20must%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20playing%20as%20a%20team%20with%20a%20common%20theme%20that%20ordinary%20Indians%20believe%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%20is%20a%20political%20commentator%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696402801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F23131246%2FThe-Wire-17.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuris-slurs-were-an-attack-on-the-constitution-of-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20MP's%20onslaught%20was%20on%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20on%20which%20MPs%20take%20their%20oath%20and%2C%20more%20particularly%2C%20on%20its%20Basic%20Structure%2C%20which%20upholds%20secularism%20as%20a%20profound%20value%20on%20which%20rests%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20integrity%2C%20unity%20and%20sovereignty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuris-slurs-were-an-attack-on-the-constitution-of-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shah%20Rukh%20apologises%20to%20fans%2C%20here's%20why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696402701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-