2Ffddlfutg_rohit-sharma-wicket-viral-shaheen-afridi_625x300_03_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwatch-your-dale-steyns-warning-to-rohit-sharma-while-facing-shaheen-afridi-in-cricket-world-cup-4440134%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20former%20South%20Africa%20pacer%20Dale%20Steyn%20has%20sent%20out%20a%20warning%20to%20Rohit%20Sharma%20while%20facing%20Shaheen%20Afridi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwatch-your-dale-steyns-warning-to-rohit-sharma-while-facing-shaheen-afridi-in-cricket-world-cup-4440134%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwatch-your-dale-steyns-warning-to-rohit-sharma-while-facing-shaheen-afridi-in-cricket-world-cup-4440134%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwatch-your-dale-steyns-warning-to-rohit-sharma-while-facing-shaheen-afridi-in-cricket-world-cup-4440134%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cricket%20World%20Cup%20Puts%20Spotlight%20On%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20has%20already%20been%20a%20pivotal%20year%20for%20India%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20another%20event%20is%20set%20to%20put%20the%20country%20in%20the%20limelight%20as%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20kicks%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20Men's%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20which%20starts%20Thursday%2C%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20global%20center%20of%20the%20sport%20has%20shifted%20firmly%20to%20India%2C%20with%20domestic%20and%20global%20sponsors%20pouring%20millions%20into%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country%20to%20chase%20the%20promise%20of%20its%201.4-billion-strong%20consumer%20base.%20India%20is%20hosting%20the%20event%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2012%20years%2C%20a%20period%20in%20which%20the%20national%20governing%20authority%20for%20cricket%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20%C2%A0richest%20sporting%20bodies%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20the%20equivalent%20of%20Mecca%20for%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ayaz%20Memon%2C%20a%20journalist%20and%20commentator%20who%20has%20tracked%20the%20sport%20over%20several%20decades.%20%26quot%3BIt%20transformed%20how%20the%20sport%20is%20played%20and%20has%20become%20the%20epicenter%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20an%20opportunity%20for%20PM%20Modi%20to%20show%20off%20his%20home%20state%20of%20Gujarat.%20In%20the%20state's%20largest%20city%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20130%2C000-seat%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20-%20which%20underwent%20an%20abrupt%20name%20change%20two%20years%20ago%20-%20will%20host%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20the%20first%20match%20when%20England%20meets%20New%20Zealand.%20Long-time%20foes%20Pakistan%20will%20play%20the%20hosts%20there%20on%20Oct.%2014%2C%20and%20the%20stadium%20will%20also%20be%20the%20location%20for%20the%20final%20on%20Nov.%2019%20and%20the%20closing%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hype%20is%20drawing%20unprecedented%20numbers%20of%20visitors%20to%20Ahmedabad%2C%20which%20has%20not%20traditionally%20been%20a%20tourist%20hotspot.%20With%20hotel%20prices%20surging%2C%20visitors%20are%20looking%20for%20alternatives%2C%20such%20as%20by%20booking%20hospital%20beds%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media%20reports.%20Many%20in%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%2C%20or%20non-resident%20Indians%2C%20are%20also%20coming%20to%20the%20city%20to%20stay%20with%20family%20for%20the%20tournament%2C%20said%20Ashish%20Koshti%2C%20who%20manages%20the%20Instagram%20account%20Amazing%20Amdavad%2C%20using%20the%20Gujarati%20pronunciation%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Cup%20also%20enables%20PM%20Modi's%20efforts%20to%20shift%20global%20perceptions%20of%20the%20city.%20After%20the%20deadly%20anti-Muslim%20riots%20in%202002%2C%20which%20took%20place%20when%20PM%20Modi%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20he%20has%20tried%20to%20make%20the%20state%20more%20business-friendly%20destination%20by%20cutting%20red%20tape%20and%20bureaucracy.%20The%20success%20of%20that%20effort%20helped%20catapult%20PM%20Modi%20to%20the%20national%20stage%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20PM%20Modi%20invited%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese%20to%20do%20a%20lap%20of%20honor%20in%20the%20Ahmedabad%20stadium%20ahead%20of%20a%20match%20between%20the%20two%20sides%2C%20and%20hosted%20a%20public%20function%20with%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20there%20in%202021.%20A%20successful%20World%20Cup%20could%20even%20bolster%20PM%20Modi's%20chances%20of%20retaining%20his%20post%20ahead%20of%20general%20elections%20slated%20for%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20has%20shown%20himself%20to%20be%20an%20apt%2C%20astute%20politician%20who%20can%20time%20things%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Binoy%20Kampmark%2C%20senior%20lecturer%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Global%2C%20Urban%20and%20Social%20Studies%20at%20RMIT%20University%20in%20Australia.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20what's%20better%20than%20using%20India's%20most%20popular%20sport%20for%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20host%20so%20many%20key%20fixtures%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20however%2C%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20in%20India%20from%20politicians%20and%20fans%20who%20question%20why%20other%20cities%20have%20been%20sidelined%2C%20particularly%20as%20Ahmedabad%20is%20not%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20center%20of%20cricket.%20In%20total%2C%2010%20cities%20in%20India%20will%20host%20matches%2C%20from%20Bengaluru%20in%20the%20south%20to%20the%20Himalayan%20town%20of%20Dharamsala%2C%20where%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20stadium%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%20just%2023%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20sports%20minister%20for%20Punjab%20wrote%20letters%20to%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20asking%20why%20the%20city%20of%20Mohali%20in%20the%20northwestern%20state%20was%20excluded%20from%20the%20list%20of%20host%20cities%2C%20addressing%20one%20to%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20who%20has%20close%20ties%20to%20Modi's%20party.%20Opposition%20lawmaker%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20similarly%20asked%20in%20a%20TV%20interview%20in%20June%20why%20his%20constituency%20of%20Thiruvananthapuram%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Kerala%20was%20left%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20can't%20just%20be%20accidental%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%20on%20NDTV%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Ahmedabad%20is%20hosting%20the%20%26quot%3Btwo%20biggest%20marquee%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20England%20vs.%20Australia%20and%20India%20vs.%20Pakistan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20the%20BJP%20declined%20to%20comment.%20The%20BCCI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20persistence%20to%20schedule%20matches%20in%20Ahmedabad%20has%20also%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20fans%20for%20poor%20planning.%20For%20example%2C%20India%20shifted%20the%20date%20for%20the%20coveted%20game%20with%20Pakistan%20by%20a%20day%20as%20it%20clashed%20with%20Navratri%2C%20a%20festival%20popular%20in%20northern%20and%20western%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20disrupting%20the%20schedule%20for%20other%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20political%20disagreements%20and%20logistical%20difficulties%2C%20Mr%20Memon%2C%20the%20cricket%20commentator%2C%20said%20that%20the%20World%20Cup%20will%20dominate%20the%20conversation%20during%20the%20next%20few%20months.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20nonstop%20baraat%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20term%20for%20an%20Indian%20wedding%20dance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20head