20Girl'%20thing%20and%20went%20to%20college%20to%20study%20genetic%20engineering%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%2C%2044%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20car%20accident%20when%20she%20was%2019%20changed%20her%20perspective%3A%20She%20realized%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20chase%20the%20typical%20American%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holding%20her%20harvest%20in%20a%20garden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6516647cc50dce00191369ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBogwalker%20with%20garden%20harvest.%3Cp%3EJenny%20Tenney%20Photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20normal%20success%20story%20of%20life%20in%20the%20US%20was%20not%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20I%20quit%20university%2C%20went%20traveling%2C%20learned%20a%20lot%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20went%20back%20to%20study%20ecological%20agriculture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20a%20deep%20calling%20to%20live%20close%20to%20the%20earth%20and%20stayed%20in%20different%20places%20around%20the%20world%2C%20like%20Spain%20and%20Guatemala%2C%20before%20she%20ended%20up%20in%20Western%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EShe%20started%20by%20living%20with%20other%20like-minded%20folk%20on%20their%20land%2C%20helping%20them%20build%20their%20projects.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20just%20happy%20to%20have%20other%20people%20living%20on%20it%20who%20wanted%20to%20do%20cool%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20time%2C%20she%20started%20living%20with%20her%20boyfriend%20on%20his%20land%20%E2%80%94%20until%20they%20broke%20up.%20This%20was%20when%20Bogwalker%20realized%20she%20needed%20the%20security%20of%20owning%20property%20and%20decided%20to%20buy%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221511%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20back%20side%20of%20a%20log%20cabin%20in%20the%20woods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6513d8bc1c099d0019ad2505%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221133%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBogwalker%20standing%20on%20the%20backside%20of%20the%20log%20cabin.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20purchased%20about%2016%20acres%20with%20two%20other%20friends%20and%20then%20split%20it%20three-way.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20plan%20was%20to%20buy%20in%20bulk%20so%20it'll%20be%20less%20expensive%20and%20also%20so%20we%20could%20guarantee%20who%20our%20neighbors%20would%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20pooled%20money%20into%20one%20account%20to%20make%20the%20purchase%20and%20did%20a%20double-closing%20to%20divide%20the%20land%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20total%20purchase%20price%20was%20%24199%2C000%20for%2016%20acres%2C%20and%20Bogwalker%20says%20she%20contributed%20%2447%2C000%20for%20seven%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20independently%20verify%20how%20much%20Bogwalker%20and%20friends%20paid%20for%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20first%20part%20of%20building%20a%20new%20house%20from%20scratch%20involves%20observing%20the%20land.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222592%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20men%20working%20on%20laying%20the%20round%20logs%20for%20the%20cabin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6516792cc50dce0019136ad3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20Bogwalker's%20friends%20helping%20her%20with%20the%20log%20cabin%20build.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20deciding%20the%20cabin's%20location%2C%20Bogwalker%20needed%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20resources%20she%20had%20on%20the%20land%20that%20she%20could%20use%20to%20build%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20all%2C%20you%20want%20to%20be%20building%20something%20that%20makes%20sense%20in%20the%20landscape%20that%20you're%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20eventually%20decided%20to%20use%20pine%20logs%20from%20the%20trees%20she%20cut%20down%20for%20the%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20pine%20trees%20that%20were%20overcrowded%20or%20in%20places%20where%20I%20was%20hoping%20to%20release%20some%20oaks%20and%20hickories%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThinning%20a%20forest%20is%20often%20helpful%20for%20the%20health%20of%20the%20forest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBogwalker%20designed%20the%20log%20cabin%20on%20her%20own.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222592%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20cabin%20as%20it's%20being%20built.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65167934c50dce0019136ad7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20cabin%20as%20it's%20being%20built.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20originally%20envisioned%20her%20cabin%20as%20a%20single-story%20building%20with%20a%20loft%2C%20but%20quickly%20changed%20her%20mind%20when%20she%20realized%20it%20wasn't%20enough%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20drew%20out%20the%20floorplan%2C%20which%20was%2012%20by%2016%2C%20and%20I%20tried%20to%20fit%20in%20little%20paper%20cut-outs%20representing%20all%20the%20things%20that%20I%20wanted%20in%20there%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20couch%20and%20my%20bed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20couldn't%20fit%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20Bogwalker%20settled%20for%20a%20two-story%20cabin%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20raw%20materials%20came%20from%20the%20land%2C%20although%20she%20had%20to%20buy%20her%20windows%2C%20doors%2C%20insulation%2C%20fixtures%2C%20and%20plumbing%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20got%20some%20of%20her%20furniture%20from%20Habitat%20for%20Humanity%20and%20bought%20the%20rest%20from%20secondhand%20sellers%20online%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20was%20tough%20doing%20things%20alone%2C%20so%20she%20hosted%20%26quot%3Bwork%20parties%26quot%3B%20where%20friends%20and%20others%20in%20the%20community%20would%20come%20to%20help.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223455%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20working%20on%20the%20logs%20of%20her%20cabin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65168b66c50dce0019136c76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222591%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20Bogwalker%20working%20on%20the%20logs%20of%20her%20cabin.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20host%20cooks%20a%20bunch%20of%20food%2C%20provides%20all%20the%20materials%20for%20the%20projects%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20and%20then%20they%20invite%20people%20to%20come%20and%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20anywhere%20between%2015%20and%2030%20people%20can%20show%20up%20for%20these%20work%20parties%2C%20including%20friends%2C%20friends%20of%20friends%2C%20and%20even%20others%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20DIY%20and%20off-grid%20living%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20big%20undertaking%20to%20build%20your%20own%20house%20as%20a%20single%20woman.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20going%20on%20for%20me%20emotionally%20as%20well%20as%20physically%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20idea%20behind%20work%20parties%20is%20mutual%20aid%2C%20she%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20number%20one%20thing%20was%20building%20friendships%20with%20people%20whom%20I%20helped%20out%20with%20various%20things%2C%20and%20they%20helped%20me%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBogwalker%20moved%20into%20her%20log%20cabin%20before%20it%20was%20completed.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20watering%20garden%20with%20log%20house%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6513d8b41c099d0019ad2501%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBogwalker%20and%20her%20garden.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20didn't%20have%20the%20finished%20floors%20up.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20plumbing%20in%20the%20cabin.%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20hydrant%20outside%20the%20cabin%20that%20I%20could%20get%20water%20with%2C%20but%20the%20whole%20place%20was%20very%20unfinished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20between%20the%20first%20cutting%20of%20the%20trees%20and%20her%20moving%20into%20the%20cabin%2C%20Bogwalker%20said.%20Prior%20to%20this%2C%20she%20had%20been%20staying%20in%20a%20tiny%20shed%20that%20she%20had%20built%20on%20her%20land%20just%20so%20she%20could%20be%20close%20to%20the%20main%20cabin%20during%20the%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20worked%20on%20the%20cabin's%20interior%20over%20the%20next%20year%2C%20and%20it%20was%20completed%20around%202013%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAfter%20two%20years%2C%20Bogwalker%20expanded%20the%20cabin%20from%20under%20400%20square%20feet%20to%20about%20700%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20standing%20next%20to%20two%20wooden%20structures%20in%20a%20forest.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6513d8b01c099d0019ad24fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENatalie%20Bogwalker%20and%20the%20log%20cabin%20that%20she%20built%20and%20expanded%20on%20over%20the%20years.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20expansion%20involved%20adding%20a%20covered%20wraparound%20porch%20to%20her%20cabin%2C%20Bogwalker%20said.%20She%20built%20the%20floor%20but%20hired%20a%20friend%20to%20do%20a%20timber%20frame%20for%20the%20porch%20cover.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20the%20same%20time%20that%20she%20found%20out%20she%20was%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'Okay%2C%20we%20need%20more%20space.'%20I%20was%20living%20with%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20so%20with%20the%20help%20of%20some%20work%20traders%2C%20apprentices%2C%20and%20work%20parties%2C%20I%20closed%20in%20a%20part%20of%20the%20covered%20porch%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20closed-in-porch%20is%20now%20a%20parlor%20%E2%80%94%20but%20back%20then%2C%20Bogwalker%20used%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbirthing%20room%26quot%3B%20where%20she%20delivered%20her%20daughter%20Hazel%20in%202016%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222366%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20parlor%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6513de7e1c099d0019ad254a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221774%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20parlor.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20I%20did%20that%2C%20I%20still%20had%20a%20pretty%20lavish%20covered%20porch%2C%20and%20I%20added%20onto%20it.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20I%20had%20a%20really%20nice%20outdoor%20sleeping%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Hazel%20turned%20three%20years%20old%20in%202019%2C%20Bogwalker%20closed%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20original%20covered%20porch%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20bedroom%20for%20her%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBogwalker%20says%20that%20her%20decision%20to%20take%20on%20this%20construction%20project%20alone%20taught%20her%20the%20importance%20of%20community.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222416%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20in%20the%20log%20cabin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6513df82eee46600193b8791%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221812%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20in%20some%20ways%20the%20hardest%20part%20was%20doing%20it%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20really%20easy%20about%20doing%20things%20as%20a%20couple%20that%20makes%20it%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20reach%20outside%20of%20that%20partnership%20and%20into%20the%20community%20to%20get%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20having%20only%20herself%20to%20rely%20on%20forced%20her%20to%20look%20to%20the%20community%20for%20assistance%20and%20support%20when%20she%20needed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENow%2C%20Bogwalker%20runs%20a%20permaculture%20and%20carpentry%20school%20called%20Wild%20Abundance.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222015%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20dining%20area%20in%20a%20log%20cabin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6513df7deee46600193b878c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221511%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20simple%20dining%20area%20consists%20of%20a%20table%20and%20two%20chairs%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20has%20now%20grown%20to%20include%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildabundance.net%2Fabout%2Fstaff%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix%20other%20staff%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildabundance.net%2Fabout%2Finstructors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erotating%20group%20of%20over%2020%20instructors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Wild%20Abunda