20was%20especially%20important%20to%20her%20that%20she%20had%20courses%20specifically%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20to%20ensure%20they%20had%20a%20comfortable%20space%20to%20get%20used%20to%20handling%20construction%20tools%20without%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20situations%20where%20women%20are%20told%20that%20they're%20not%20good%20at%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Bogwalker%20said%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20just%20makes%20my%20heart%20sing%20when%20I%20see%20women%20coming%20into%20their%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBogwalker%20has%20some%20advice%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20build%20their%20own%20house%3A%20Start%20small.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222210%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20porch%20was%20created%20by%20extending%20the%20original%20blueprint%20of%20the%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6513def91c099d0019ad2550%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221658%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20back%20porch%20was%20created%20by%20extending%20the%20original%20blueprint%20of%20the%20house.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Wild%20Abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEspecially%20for%20those%20who%20have%20never%20done%20similar%20projects%20before%2C%20it'll%20be%20wiser%20to%20start%20with%20a%20smaller%20floorplan%20design%20and%20build%20on%20it%20over%20time%2C%20Bogwalker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20keep%20an%20open%20mind%20when%20faced%20with%20any%20challenges%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20making%20the%20best%20choice%20you%20can%20and%20having%20the%20understanding%20that%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20anticipate%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiy-construction-log-cabin-woman-sustainable-rural-living-scho