ater%20causes%20a%20burning%20sensation%20in%20her%20throat%20and%20body%20so%20the%2025-year-old%20claims%20she%20drinks%20milk%20because%20the%20fats%20and%20proteins%20and%20sugars%20in%20milk%20help%20the%20water%20molecules%20to%20%26quot%3Bsneak%20past%26quot%3B%20her%20immune%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%20Karen%20Hansen-Smith%20is%20a%20doctor%20who%20has%20seen%20many%20rare%20illnesses%2C%20but%20watching%20her%20own%20daughter%20suffer%20is%20very%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20a%20little%20guilty%20as%20a%20mom%20for%20not%20having%20seen%20when%20she%20would%20get%20out%20of%20the%20shower%20that%20she%20had%20hives%20and%20figuring%20it%20out%20way%20earlier%20that%20it%20was%20a%20water%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20heartbreaking.%20I%20still%20have%20my%20daughter.%20But%20she's%20not%20living%20the%20life%20she%20wanted%20to%20live%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Hansen-Smith%20has%20an%20older%20sister%20who%20does%20not%20have%20a%20water%20allergy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20has%20set%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Ftessa-hansen-smiths-medical-bills%5C%22%3EGoFundMe%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20pay%20the%20bill%20for%20her%20recent%20hospital%20stay%2C%20which%20rose%20to%20%248%2C000%20(Rs%206.65%20lakh).%20She%20has%20thanked%20all%20her%20supporters%20for%20helping%20them%20collect%20%2410%2C000%20in%20just%20three%20months%2C%20which%20will%20also%20help%20her%20in%20doctor's%20appointments%2C%20follow%20ups%20and%20physical%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20has%20had%20her%20tough%20moments.%20Ms%20Hansen-Smith%20said%20the%20scepticism%20of%20people%20around%20her%20was%20more%20painful%20than%20the%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20did%20tell%20people%20about%20it%20in%20college%2C%20I%20would%20have%20people%20try%20to%20purposely%20splash%20water%20on%20