0recorded%2024%20deaths%20in%20a%20matter%20of%2024%20hours.%20In%20a%20matter%20of%2048%20hours%2C%20a%20total%20of%2059%20have%20died%20allegedly%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20medicines%20and%20availability%20of%20doctors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F04%2F59-die-in-two-maharashtra-govt-hospitals-in-last-48-hours-cm-orders-high-level-probe-2620505.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20more%20are%20said%20to%20be%20in%20critical%20condition%2C%20in%20want%20of%20life-saving%20drugs%20and%20medical%20help.%20As%20the%20death%20toll%20mounts%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20has%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20by%20a%20three-member%20expert%20committee.%20Hasan%20Mushrif%2C%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20medical%20education%20minister%2C%20is%20also%20scheduled%20to%20visit%20the%20hospitals%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20last%20count%2C%2024%20died%20in%20Ghati%20Hospital%20in%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20and%2035%20in%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%20Hospital%20in%20Nanded.%20Among%20the%20deceased%20at%20the%20Nanded%20hospital%2C%2016%20were%20infants.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20guilty%20will%20be%20punished%20after%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20probe%20committee.%20We%20have%20taken%20serious%20cognisance%20of%20these%20incidents%20and%20sent%20a%20team%20of%20minister%2C%20secretary%2C%20and%20officers%20to%20visit%20the%20hospitals%20in%20Nanded%20and%20Ghati%20in%20Aurangabad%20and%20submit%20a%20report%2C%E2%80%9D%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20officials%20initially%20tried%20to%20downplay%20the%20incident%20in%20Nanded%2C%20district%20information%20office%20(DIO)%20confirmed%20the%20fatalities%2C%20urging%20people%20not%20to%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20facts%20related%20to%20the%20death%20of%20patients%20at%20Dr.%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%20Government%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20is%20as%20follows%3A%2024%20deaths%20between%20September%2030%20and%20October%201%3B%20seven%20deaths%20between%20October%201%20and%202.%20Please%20do%20not%20panic.%20A%20team%20of%20doctors%20is%20ready%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20DIO%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmaharashtra-new-born-deaths-aurangabad-nanded%2Farticle67374944.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%2C%20there%20are%2070%20other%20people%20at%20the%20Nanded%20hospital%20who%20are%20in%20critical%20condition.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%2070%20other%20people%20in%20serious%20condition.%20We%20came%20to%20know%20that%20medicine%20supply%20and%20recruitment%20of%20doctors%20has%20been%20stuck%20due%20to%20unknown%20reasons%20and%20that%20cost%20the%20lives%20of%20several%20people.%20The%20state%20government%20should%20fix%20the%20responsibility%20and%20improve%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ETNIE%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Congress%20president%2C%20Nana%20Patole%2C%20accused%20the%20public%20health%20department%20authorities%20of%20demanding%20a%2040%25%20commission%20in%20the%20contracts%20pertaining%20to%20medical%20supplies%2C%20which%20he%20alleged%20was%20the%20reason%20for%20deaths.%20He%20said%20no%20lesson%20has%20been%20learnt%20by%20the%20Shinde%20government%20even%20after%20T%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fthane-hospital-deaths-eknath-shinde-police-probe-death-toll-8891192%2F%5C%22%3Ehane%20Municipal%20Corporation%20hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%20recorded%2018%20deaths%20in%20the%20second%20week%20of%20August%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20public%20health%20system%20in%20the%20state%20is%20suffering%20from%20the%20disease%20of%20corruption%20and%20the%20entire%20system%20is%20on%20a%20ventilator.%20There%20aren%E2%80%99t%20enough%20doctors%20and%20staff%20in%20government%20hospitals%20and%20there%20is%20also%20a%20shortage%20of%20medicines.%20The%20equipment%20in%20the%20hospitals%20is%20dysfunctional%20and%20lying%20idle.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20state%20of%20health%20services%20in%20major%20cities%2C%20one%20can%20only%20imagine%20the%20condition%20in%20rural%20hospitals.%20A%20culpable%20homicide%20case%20under%20IPC%20302%20should%20be%20filed%20against%20the%20state%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patole%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F04%2F59-die-in-two-maharashtra-govt-hospitals-in-last-48-hours-cm-orders-high-level-probe-2620505.html%5C%22%3Edemanded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20chief%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20two%20months%20ago%2C%20there%20was%20an%20unfortunate%20incident%20where%2018%20people%20died%20in%20a%20single%20night%20in%20Kalwa%20Hospital%20of%20Thane%20Municipal%20Corporation.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20not%20taking%20this%20incident%20seriously%2C%20such%20a%20very%20serious%20incident%20was%20repeated%20in%20the%20government%20hospital%20in%20Nanded.%20This%20shows%20the%20failure%20of%20government%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmaharashtra-new-born-deaths-aurangabad-nanded%2Farticle67374944.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20national%20president%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20called%20for%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20deaths.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20news%20of%20the%20death%20of%2024%20patients%2C%20including%2012%20infants%2C%20in%20a%20civil%20hospital%20in%20Nanded%2C%20Maharashtra%20is%20extremely%20painful%2C%20serious%20and%20worrying.%20It%20is%20being%20said%20that%20these%20patients%20died%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20medicines%20and%20t