the%20categories%2C%20including%20fees%20for%20up%20to%206%20months%2C%202%2C%205%20and%2010-year%20visit%20visas%3B%20the%20majority%20of%20fees%20for%20entry%20clearance%20and%20certain%20applications%20for%20leave%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20including%20those%20for%20work%20and%20study%3B%20fees%20for%20indefinite%20leave%20to%20enter%20and%20indefinite%20leave%20to%20remain%3B%20health%20and%20care%20visa%3B%20fees%20in%20relation%20to%20certificates%20of%20sponsorship%20and%20confirmation%20of%20acceptance%20for%20studies%3B%20and%20applications%20to%20register%20and%20naturalise%20as%20a%20British%20Citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20right%20and%20fair%20to%20increase%20visa%20application%20fees%20so%20we%20can%20fund%20vital%20public%20services%20and%20allow%20wider%20funding%20to%20contribute%20to%20public%20sector%20pay%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Home%20Office%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUK%20visa%20application%20fees%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20October%204%2C%20the%20new%20fee%20structure%20for%20UK%20visas%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20for%20foreigners%2C%20including%20Indians.%20The%20cost%20of%20UK%20visas%20will%20go%20up%20for%20students%2C%20skilled%20workers%20and%20immigrants.%20As%20per%20the%20official%20site%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20family%2C%20settlement%20and%20citizenship%20visas%20will%20increase%20by%2020%25%2C%20while%20the%20cost%20of%20work%20and%20visit%20visas%20will%20increase%20by%2015%25.%20The%20immigration%20health%20surcharge%20(IHS)%20will%20also%20rise%20to%20GBP%201%2C035%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20visa%20charge%20for%20students%2C%20including%20child%20students%20and%20dependents%2C%20will%20rise%20to%20GBP%20490.%20However%2C%20the%20UK%20government%20said%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20rise%20in%20visa%20fees%20for%20short-term%20courses%20where%20students%20study%20English%20for%20more%20than%206%20months%20but%20no%20more%20than%2011%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20skilled%20workers%2C%20where%20a%20certificate%20sponsorship%20has%20been%20issued%20for%20three%20years%20or%20less%2C%20the%20visa%20price%20will%20be%20GBP%20719%20(Rs%2065%2C000).%20But%20if%20the%20sponsorship%20certificate%20has%20been%20given%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years%2C%20the%20immigration%20fee%20will%20be%20GBP%201420%2C%20which%20is%20approximately%20Rs%20129%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20visa%20price%20has%20also%20been%20increased%20for%20skilled%20workers%20in%20shortage%20occupations%20where%20a%20certificate%20of%20sponsorship%20has%20been%20given%20for%20three%20years%20or%20less.%20They%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20GBP%20551%2C%20which%20is%20nearly%20Rs%2050%2C351.%20If%20the%20sponsorship%20certificate%20has%20been%20in%20effect%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years%2C%20the%20immigration%20fee%20will%20cost%20GBP%201%2C084%20or%20Rs%2099%2C125.%20Moreover%2C%20people%20who%20desire%20a%20visa%2C%20permission%20to%20stay%20or%20citizenship%20in%20the%20UK%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696396620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-01%2Fuk-visa-generic_650x400_51453218458.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-visa-fee-hike-effective-from-today-heres-how-itll-impact-students-workers-and-visitors-4447871%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20visa%20hike%20announced%20by%20the%20British%20government%20will%20be%20effective%20from%20today.%20With%20this%2C%20a%20visit%20visa%20to%20the%20UK%20for%20under%20six%20months%20will%20cost%20GBP%20(Great%20Britain%20Pound)%2015%20more%20and%20a%20student%20visa%20will%20be%20GBP%20127%20more%20expensive%20for%20travellers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-visa-fee-hike-effective-from-today-heres-how-itll-impact-students-workers-and-visitors-4447871%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com