20best%20when%20they%20remain%20private%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20Global%20News.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIn%20moments%20of%20tensions%20-%20because%20indeed%20there%20are%20tensions%20between%20both%20our%20governments%20more%20than%20ever%20-%20it's%20important%20that%20diplomats%20be%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20a%20strong%20diplomatic%20footprint%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIn%20June%2C%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20masked%20gunmen%20in%20British%20Columbia.%20The%2045-year-old%20was%20a%20designated%20terrorist%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20couple%20of%20weeks%20back%2C%20Trudeau%20alleged%20India's%20role%20in%20Nijjar's%20killing.%20%26quot%3BCanadian%20security%20agencies%20have%20been%20actively%20pursuing%20credible%20allegations%20of%20a%20potential%20link%20between%20agents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BAny%20involvement%20of%20a%20foreign%20government%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20is%20an%20unacceptable%20violation%20of%20our%20sovereignty.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20set%20off%20a%20diplomatic%20storm.%20India%20termed%20the%20allegations%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20both%20sides%20expelled%20senior%20diplomats%20and%20issuing%20travel%20advisories.%20While%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20the%20Financial%20Times%20report%20on%20asking%20Canadian%20diplomats%20to%20leaves%2C%20it%20had%20earlier%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bparity%26quot%3B%20in%20number%20and%20rank%20of%20diplomats%20each%20country%20deploys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%C2%A0Trudeau's%20big%20charge%20against%20India%20came%20shortly%20after%20his%20trip%20to%20New%20Delhi%20for%20the%20G20%20summit.%20India%20sent%20a%20strong%20message%20during%20the%20summit%2C%20expressing%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20concerns%20about%20continuing%20anti-India%20activities%20of%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Canada%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20The%20concerns%20were%20raised%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit.%20In%20response%2C%20Trudeau%20said%20his%20country%20%26quot%3Bwill%20always%20defend%20freedom%20of%20expression%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20few%20do%20not%20represent%20Canada%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20Canadian%20government's%20allegations%20need%20to%20be%20probed.%20The%20matter%20was%20discussed%20when%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20met%20last%20week%2C%20John%20Kirby%2C%20Coordinator%20for%20Strategic%20Communications%20at%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20told%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20certainly%20leave%20it%20to%20those%20two%20countries%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20bilateral%20relationship.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20clear%2C%20these%20allegations%20are%20serious%2C%20they%20need%20to%20be%20fully%20investigated%20and%20of%20course%2C%20as%20we've%20said%20before%2C%20we%20urge%20India%20to%20participate%20actively%20in%20that%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20added.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20Canadian%20officials%20had%20sought%20public%20condemnation%20of%20Nijjar's%20murder%20from%20allies%20ahead%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20but%20found%20them%20reluctant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696396020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fseuhqis_pm-modi-justin-trudeau-ani_625x300_22_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-ties-justin-trudeau-hardeep-singh-nijjar-talks-on-diplomats-with-india-in-private-canada-ministeramidface-off-4447882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20move%20towards%20defusing%20tension%20with%20India%2C%20Canada%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20has%20said%20Ottawa%20is%20not%20looking%20to%20%26quot%3Bescalate%26quot%3B.%20His%20government%20has%20indicated%20they%20are%20holding%20%26quot%3Bprivate%26quot%3B%20talks%20to%20maintain%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20diplomatic%20footprint%26quot%3B%20in%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-ties-justin-trudeau-hardeep-singh-nijjar-talks-on-diplomats-with-india-in-private-canada-ministeramidface-off-4447882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-ties-justin-trudeau-hardeep-singh-nijjar-talks-on-diplomats-with-india-in-private-canada-ministeramidface-off-4447882%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-ties-justin-trudeau-hardeep-singh-nijjar-talks-on-diplomats-with-india-in-private-canada-ministeramidface-off-4447882%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TikTok%3A%20Social%20media%20app%20shuts%20shop%20after%20Indonesia%20ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696395923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2AB4%2Fproduction%2F_131323901_gettyimages-1683250175.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67002545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20country's%20government%20banned%20the%20sale%20of%20goods%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20protect%20physical%20stores.%22%