said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ED%20raid%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Sanjay%20Singh%20being%20vocal%20about%20the%20Adani%20issue%20and%20the%20black%20money%20invested%20in%20his%20company.%20Neither%20they%20(ED)%20found%20anything%20earlier%2C%20nor%20they%20will%20find%20anything%20today.%20None%20of%20us%20is%20afraid.%E2%80%9D%20AAP%20tweeted%20an%20old%20video%20of%20Singh%20in%20which%20he%20is%20seen%20campaigning%20against%20corruption%2C%20and%20said%20the%20leader%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20honesty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%88%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B9%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%20%F0%9F%94%A5%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSanjaySingh%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SanjaySingh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzXcvvxD3Bk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzXcvvxD3Bk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20AAP%20(%40AamAadmiParty)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAamAadmiParty%2Fstatus%2F1709409008724095377%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20leader%20Manoj%20Jha%20too%20condemned%20the%20ED%20action%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftimesofindia%2Fstatus%2F1709423779028533583%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20sad%2C%20but%20not%20surprising.%20Now%20this%20series%20will%20continue%20till%20the%20election.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20have%20made%20the%20formal%20announcement%20for%20the%202024%20elections.%20Yesterday%2C%20a%20raid%20was%20on%20NewsClick%20and%20all%20the%20journalists%2C%20today%20on%20Sanjay%20Singh%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20case%2C%20which%20was%20registered%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20is%20based%20on%20a%20CBI%C2%A0FIR%20filed%20in%20August.%20The%20CBI%20had%20booked%20Sisodia%2C%20three%20excise%20department%20officials%20and%20several%20vendors%20and%20distributors%20among%20the%2015%20accused%20it%20had%20arraigned%20in%20its%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696394202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04100557%2FF7CDMUjXoAAmsqX.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fenforcement-directorate-conducts-searches-at-aap-mp-sanjay-singhs-house%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20has%20maintained%20that%20this%20case%20is%20political%20vendetta%20being%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20using%20the%20central%20agencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fenforcement-directorate-conducts-searches-at-aap-mp-sanjay-singhs-house%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy's%20Removal%2C%20What's%20Next%20For%20US%20House%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20conservative%20revolt%20that%20brought%20down%20now-former%20House%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20has%20left%20the%20chamber%20in%20a%20state%20of%20paralysis%20until%20a%20new%20speaker%20is%20found.%20That%20raises%20the%20chances%20of%20a%20US%20government%20shutdown%20next%20month%20and%20a%20delay%20in%20further%20Ukraine%20assistance.%20Here%20are%20the%20next%20steps%20the%20House%20faces%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho's%20now%20in%20charge%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatrick%20McHenry%2C%20Republican%20of%20North%20Carolina%2C%20is%20now%20the%20speaker%20pro-tem.%20Under%20the%20rules%2C%20he%20is%20limited%20in%20his%20powers%20and%20likely%20unable%20to%20conduct%20any%20normal%20legislative%20business.%20His%20primary%20task%20is%20to%20organize%20the%20election%20of%20a%20new%20speaker.%20If%20an%20impasse%20over%20choosing%20someone%20for%20that%20position%20ensues%2C%20the%20House%20could%20grant%20McHenry%20time-limited%20authority%20to%20preside%20over%20debate%20and%20votes%20on%20ordinary%20bills.%20That%2C%20however%2C%20would%20take%20a%20majority%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20will%20a%20new%20speaker%20be%20chosen%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMcCarthy's%20decision%20not%20to%20run%20again%20speeds%20up%20the%20process%20of%20finding%20a%20new%20speaker.%20If%20he%20had%20tried%20a%20war%20of%20attrition%20with%20the%20eight%20Republican%20opponents%20who%20brought%20about%20his%20downfall%2C%20he%20would%20have%20dragged%20out%20the%20process.%20McHenry%20has%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20hold%20speaker%20elections%20Wednesday%2C%20Oct.%2011.%20The%20House%20Republican%20majority%20will%20hold%20a%20closed-door%20forum%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20where%20candidates%20can%20put%20themselves%20up%20for%20the%20job.%20The%20conference%20would%20then%20vote%20to%20select%20their%20nominee%20for%20speakership.%20If%20a%20strong%20candidate%20emerges%2C%20McHenry%20plans%20to%20proceed%20with%20votes%20on%20the%20floor%20to%20install%20a%20new%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20the%20speaker%20election%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20will%20be%20conducted%20by%20a%20roll%20call%20vote%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House.%20With%20two%20vacancies%20in%20the%20435-member%20chamber%2C%20a%20candidate%20must%20get%20217%20votes%20to%20win%20if%20all%20members%20showed%20up%20and%20voted%2C%20and%20none%20abstained%20by%20voting%20%26quot%3Bpresent.%26quot%3B%20In%20January%2C%20McCarthy%20became%20speaker%2C%20but%20only%20after%20a%20record%2015%20ballots.%20Uniting%20the%20Republican%20conference%20behind%20a%20consensus%20candidate%20will%20be%20difficult%2C%20given%20the%20differing%20goals%20of%20swing-district%20moderates%20and%20ultraconservatives%20who%20ousted%20McCarthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20will%20run%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPossible%20candidates%20to%20replace%20McCarthy%20include%20senior%20leadership%20members%20Majority%20Leader%20Steve%20Scalise%20of%20Louisiana%2C%20Majority%20Whip%20Tom%20Emmer%20of%20Minnesota%20or%20Conference%20Chair%20Elise%20Stefanik%20of%20New%20York.%20The%20conservative%20Freedom%20Caucus%20could%20put%20forward%20its%20own%20candidate%2C%20although%20one%20potential%20prospect%2C%20Chip%20Roy%20of%20Texas%2C%20says%20he%20isn't%20interested.%20Moderates%20could%20also%20angle%20for%20their%20own%20candidate%20like%20Brian%20Fitzpatrick%20of%20Pennsylvania.%20Republican%20Study%20Committee%20Chairman%20Kevin%20Hern%20and%20Freedom%20Caucus%20member%20Jim%20Jordan%20are%20possible%20candidates.%20Some%20lawmakers%20are%20advocating%20for%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20though%20that%20is%20a%20long%20shot.%20It%20is%20possible%20because%20the%20speaker%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20member%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Democrats%20have%20an%20easier%20path%20forward.%20They%20are%20expected%20to%20stick%20to%20nominating%20Hakeem%20Jeffries%20of%20New%20York%2C%20the%20minority%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20the%20House%20do%20in%20the%20meantime%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20has%20recessed%20until%20Oct.%2010%20with%20members%20heading%20home%20to%20their%20districts.%20Until%20a%20new%20speaker%20is%20chosen%2C%20it%20likely%20cannot%20conduct%20votes%20on%20legislation%20like%20pending%20fiscal%202024%20spending%20bills.%20The%20rules%20have%20not%20been%20tested%20but%20the%20House%20rules-keeper%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20grant%20McHenry%20full%20speaker%20powers%20based%20on%20the%20li