come%2030%25%20more%20productive%20because%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20intend%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20a%20single%20one.%20I'll%20get%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20the%20company's%20programmers%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F10%2F03%2Fibms-ceo-automate-repetitive-white-collar-job-not-cutting-workers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFortune's%20CEO%20Initiative%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrishna%20further%20said%20that%20his%20company%20was%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20software%20engineering%20and%20sales%20roles%20in%20the%20next%20three%20to%20four%20years%20but%20expected%20to%20phase%20out%20back-office%20HR%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20more%20jobs%20were%20created%20than%20lost%20due%20to%20AI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20increase%20was%20like%208%2C000.%20The%20decrease%20was%20like%20800.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thing%20you%20can%20automate%20is%20a%20repetitive%2C%20white-collar%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Krishna.%20He%20added%20that%20while%20AI%20could%20take%20over%2010%20to%2020%25%20of%20%26quot%3Blower%20level%26quot%3B%20tasks%2C%20it%20was%20unlikely%20to%20automate%20away%20somebody's%20entire%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrishna%20previously%20said%20his%20company%20would%20halt%20hiring%20for%20certain%20jobs%20that%20could%20be%20replaced%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20easily%20see%2030%25%20of%20that%20getting%20replaced%20by%20AI%20and%20automation%20over%20a%20five-year%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20Krishna%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fibm-halts-hiring-for-7800-jobs-that-could-be-replaced-by-ai-report-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%20%E2%80%94%20a%20figure%20that%20equates%20to%20around%207%2C800%20jobs%20at%20IBM's%20human%20resources%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20there%20is