has%20been%20the%20looting%20of%20state%20armouries.%20In%20total%2C%20nearly%204%2C500%20weapons%20and%20around%20650%2C000%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%20have%20gone%20missing.%20Of%20these%2C%20only%201%2C500%20arms%20and%20around%2015%2C000%20pieces%20of%20ammunition%20have%20been%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeep%20divisions%20have%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbuffer%20zones%E2%80%9D%20between%20Meitei-dominated%20and%20Kuki-dominated%20areas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20are%20not%20able%20to%20access%20these%20zones.%20Between%20Churachandpur%20and%20Imphal%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-police-kept-out-of-buffer-zones-550232%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20four%20barricades%20%E2%80%93%20manned%20by%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20second%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20the%20third%20by%20the%20BSF%20and%20the%20last%20one%20by%20the%20CRPF%20(all%20central%20forces).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20media%20these%20locations%20with%20heavy%20presence%20of%20Central%20forces%20are%20known%20as%20buffer%20zones.%20We%20call%20them%20hotspots.%20The%20multiple%20barriers%20set%20up%20before%20Churachandpur%20is%20one%20of%20those%20hotspots.%20There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20such%20hotspots%20across%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kuldiep%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20CRPF%20DG%20who%20has%20been%20appointed%20Security%20Adviser%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20buffer%20zones%2C%20combines%20with%20widespread%20internal%20migration%2C%20have%20also%20reportedly%20complicated%20the%20Manipur%20Police%E2%80%99s%20investigations%20and%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696393299000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffive-months-into-manipur-co