telephones%20%E2%80%93%20of%20dozens%20of%20journalists%20were%20seized%20by%20the%20police.%20Those%20targeted%20included%20some%20who%20have%20just%20had%20fleeting%20contact%20with%20the%20news%20portal%20as%20occasional%20contributors.%20Authors%2C%20journalists%2C%20satirists%2C%20historians%20and%20scientists%20associated%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20all%20raided%20in%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20show%20them%20where%20unbridled%20power%20lay.%20No%20proper%20seizure%20memos%20or%20hash%20values%20for%20the%20devices%20were%20given.%20It%20was%20a%20brute%20exercise%20of%20power.%20The%20intent%20appeared%20to%20be%20to%20assert%20authority%20and%20control%2C%20and%20finally%20a%20lock%20was%20placed%20at%20the%20news%20portal%E2%80%99s%20office.%20A%20total%20of%2046%20persons%20were%20questioned%20by%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20dark%20year%20in%20India%20for%20those%20who%20stand%20for%20a%20free%20press.%20The%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Index%20ranks%20India%20at%20161%2C%20in%20the%20bottom%20twenty%20of%20the%20180%20countries%20whose%20status%20it%20assesses.%20The%20fall%20has%20been%20immense%20and%20sharp%20since%202015.%20India%20is%20also%20the%20global%20internet%20shutdown%20capital%2C%20with%20by%20far%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20internet%20closures%20per%20year%20amongst%20all%20democracies.%20India%20has%20displayed%20record%20democratic%20backsliding%2C%20and%20the%20state%20of%20the%20press%20is%20a%20vital%20component%20of%20the%20deterioration.%20Unless%20he%20means%20it%20ironically%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20still%20never%20fails%20to%20talk%20about%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20straight%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attempt%20to%20tighten%20the%20noose%20around%20digital%20and%20independent%20media%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20single%20press%20conference%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C