20speed%20is%20currently%2065.45%20knots%20%E2%80%94%20SP80%20is%20gunning%20for%2080%20knots%2C%20or%2092%20mph.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20SP80%20boat%20was%20displayed%20at%20this%20year's%20Monaco%20Yacht%20Show.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20slender%20frame%2C%20white%20exterior%2C%20and%20extraterrestrial%20vibe%2C%20SP80%20is%20looking%20to%20break%20the%20record%20for%20the%20world's%20fastest%20sailboat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20SP80%20boat%2C%20displayed%20%26quot%3Bready-to-sail%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-yacht-monaco-show-photos-microsoft-paul-allen-photos-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMonaco%20Yacht%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20looks%20like%20it%20would%20be%20powered%20by%20rocket%20fuel%2C%20a%20giant%20kite%20pulls%20the%20vessel%20along%20with%20the%20wind%2C%20Laura%20Manon%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20SP80%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rendering%20of%20a%20black%20boat%20on%20the%20water%20being%20pulled%20by%20a%20large%20white%20kite%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651b631e2ce014759e72ee58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20the%20SP80%20boat%20being%20pulled%20by%20a%20kite%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20SP80%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20talked%20to%20hundreds%20of%20people%20over%20the%20week%2C%20and%20they%20were%20all%20amazed%20that%20it%20was%20a%20sailboat%20with%20no%20engine%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20Manon%20said%20of%20the%20yacht%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManon%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BPeople%20in%20Monaco%20said%20it%20looked%20more%20like%20a%20submarine%20or%20an%20airplane%2C%20and%20someone%20even%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20drone!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20company%2C%20started%20by%20pals%20Mayeul%20van