%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FGoing-Infinite-Rise-Fall-Tycoon%252Fdp%252F1324074337%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20biography%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20FTX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Short%26quot%3B%20author%20Michael%20Lewis'%20new%20book%20on%20Bankman-Fried%20hit%20the%20shelves.%20The%20book%20includes%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-biography-michael-lewis-tom-brady-jail-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20revelations%20about%20the%20FTX%20cofounder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20details%20on%20his%20past%20relationship%20with%20the%20former%20Alameda%20Research%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20memo%2C%20which%20was%20published%20in%20the%20book%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20laid%20out%20a%20slew%20of%20cons%20for%20a%20sexual%20relationship%20with%20him%2C%20which%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bharrowing%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20he%20has%20difficulty%20respecting%20other%20people%20and%20often%20wants%20to%20spend%20time%20by%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%20I%20don't%20really%20have%20a%20soul%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20wrote%20in%20the%20memo%2C%20according%20to%20Lewis.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20pretty%20decent%20argument%20that%20my%20empathy%20is%20fake%2C%20my%20feelings%20are%20fake%2C%20my%20facial%20reactions%20are%20fake.%20I%20don't%20feel%20happiness.%20What's%20the%20point%20in%20dating%20someone%20who%20you%20physically%20can't%20make%20happy%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20FTX%20cofounder%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20cons%20included%20concerns%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bpower%20dynamics%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20relationship%20%E2%80%94%20Ellison%20at%20the%20time%20was%20serving%20as%20CEO%20of%20another%20of%20Bankman-Fried's%20companies%2C%20Alameda%20Research%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20his%20lack%20of%20empathy%20and%20%26quot%3Bhistory%20of%20getting%20bored%20and%20claustrophobic.%26quot%3B