%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20American%20history%2C%20House%20lawmakers%20have%20ejected%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20from%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20Rep.%20Matt%20Gaetz's%20gambit%20was%20successful%2C%20House%20lawmakers%20must%20find%20a%20new%20leader%20of%20the%20chamber%20who%20is%20also%20second-in-line%20for%20the%20presidency.%20The%20nation%20could%20very%20well%20be%20in%20a%20multi-day%20drama%20like%20the%20five%20days%20in%20January%20that%20ultimately%20ended%20with%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20as%20speaker.%20And%20yes%2C%20this%20entire%20saga%20could%20also%20end%20with%20McCarthy%20retaking%20the%20gavel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20show%20of%20loyalty%2C%20every%20member%20of%20House%20leadership%20on%20this%20list%2C%20including%20Reps.%20Tom%20Emmer%2C%20Steve%20Scalise%2C%20and%20Elise%20Stefanik%2C%20pleaded%20with%20their%20colleagues%20to%20keep%20McCarthy%20in%20his%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHere's%20who%20reportedly%20could%20step%20up%20to%20lead%20the%20House%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%3ETom%20Emmer%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tom%20Emmer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c6ab7617692f0d03e1d2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Tom%20Emmer%2C%20a%20Minnesota%20Republican%3Cp%3ENathan%20Howard%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmmer%20is%20the%20No.%203%20House%20Republican%20and%20formerly%20led%20the%20House%20GOP's%20campaign%20arm.%20He%20was%20at%20the%20center%20of%20talks%20that%20broke%20the%20days-long%20deadlock%20that%20led%20to%20McCarthy%20finally%20winning%20the%20speakership%20in%20January.%20As%20Majority%20Whip%2C%20it%20is%20his%20main%20job%20to%20help%20count%20the%20votes%20and%20find%20ways%20to%20work%20within%20the%20Republican%20Party's%20slim%20five-seat%20majority%20(it's%20even%20smaller%20at%20the%20moment%20due%20to