%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRzttSFnvC0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRzttSFnvC0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1709191398778376552%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20elections%2C%20KCR%20came%20to%20meet%20me%20in%20Delhi.%20He%20praised%20me%20a%20lot.%20He%20asked%20me%20to%20extend%20support%20to%20him.%20He%20wanted%20to%20join%20the%20NDA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%20The%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20he%20told%20the%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20of%20your%20deeds%2C%20Modi%20cannot%20join%20hands%20with%20you%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20and%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(MIM)%20joined%20hands%20for%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20mayoral%20polls.%20While%20BJP%20won%2048%20seats%2C%20the%20BRS%20won%2056%20and%20MIM%2043.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20while%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20gave%20money%20to%20the%20BRS%20government%20in%20Telangana%20for%20development%2C%20the%20latter%20%E2%80%9Clooted%20the%20money%20that%20was%20sent%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20claim%2C%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20Telangana%20IT%20minister%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20(KTR)%20said%20that%20the%20BRS%20does%20not%20have%20the%20misfortune%20of%20having%20to%20join%20the%20NDA.%20%E2%80%9CKCR%20is%20a%20fighter.%20He%20will%20never%20join%20hands%20with%20a%20cheater%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rama%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNDA%20is%20a%20sinking%20ship.%20Allies%20like%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%2C%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dali%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20have%20left%20the%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20real%20%E2%80%9Cpartners%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20alliance%20were%20%C2%A0investigating%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20contributed%20nothing%20to%20the%20development%20of%20Telangana%20since%20it%20was%20formed%20in%202014%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20people%20would%20ensure%20that%20the%20BJP%20wins%20nothing%20in%20the%20upcoming%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20fight%20the%20BJP%20electorally%20and%20defeat%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rama%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBRS%20Working%20President%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20reacts%20to%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20Telangana%20CM%20KC%20Rao%20wanted%20to%20join%20NDA%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6This%20PM%20is%20so%20inconsistent%2C%20he%20says%20that%20BRS%20funded%3Cbr%3E%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20that%20he%20has%20not%20allowed%20us%20in%20NDA.%20Have%20we%20been%20bitten%20by%20a%20mad%20dog%20that%20we%20will%20join%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPKyTBSGNZ0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPKyTBSGNZ0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1709204293377724758%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Congress%20leader%20Revanth%20Reddy%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20revealation%20showed%20that%20Modi%20and%20KCR%20were%20working%20together%20in%20secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696344293000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03200823%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-8.07.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%