n%20an%20area%20of%203%2C200%20square%20feet.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20cosmopolitan%20cities%20to%20rural%20tranquility%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Madhulika%20(43)%20is%20a%20computer%20science%20graduate%2C%20Ashis%20(42)%20pursued%20civil%20engineering.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20they%20worked%20with%20several%20non-profit%20organisations%20when%20their%20interests%20shifted%20to%20rural%20development%2C%20social%2C%20and%20environmental%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMadhulika%2C%20who%20pursued%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20telecommunications%20from%20the%20US%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20our%20marriage%2C%20we%20have%20lived%20in%20different%20cities%20and%20countries%20as%20well.%20But%20we%20had%20decided%20to%20settle%20in%20Rajasthan%20while%20we%20were%20still%20in%20college.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20settling%20in%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Dungarpur%20in%20South%20Rajasthan%2C%20they%20lived%20in%20several%20cities%20like%20Anantpur%2C%20Udaipur%2C%20Chittorgarh%2C%20Bhilwara%2C%20and%20a%20few%20villages.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20lived%20in%20state%20capitals%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20quiet%20place%20without%20traffic%20noise.%20We%20discovered%20this%20town%20to%20be%20peaceful%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashis%2C%20who%20currently%20heads%20an%20NGO%20Sambhaav%20Trust%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20couple%20purchased%20the%20land%20and%20began%20researching%20ways%20to%20create%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244161%2Fthese-10-eco-friendly-homes-will-inspire-you-to-live-sustainably%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentally%20friendly%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20sustainable%20house.%20They%20spent%2010%20months%20on%20this%20research%2C%20during%20which%