%20reported%20on%20matters%20like%20the%202020%20Delhi%20riots%2C%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20laws%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20journalists%20and%20commentators%20associated%20with%20the%20online%20news%20portal%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell%20for%20questioning.%20The%20residences%20of%20many%20others%20were%20raided%2C%20and%20the%20police%20seized%20devices%20such%20as%20laptops%20and%20phones%20without%20providing%20seizure%20memos%20with%20a%20hash%20value%20%E2%80%93%20a%20number%20unique%20to%20the%20precise%20data%20on%20the%20device%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20seizure%20which%20courts%20can%20refer%20to%20in%20the%20event%20of%20accusations%20of%20tampering%20against%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVeteran%20journalist%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20who%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20special%20cell%E2%80%99s%20office%20at%20around%208%20am%20and%20released%20around%206%20pm%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20revealed%20the%20line%20of%20questioning%20that%20the%20police%20adopted.%20He%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20had%20called%20a%20US%20number%20which%20belongs%20to%20his%20brother-in-law%20and%20if%20he%20uses%20the%20Signal%20messaging%20app.%20He%20wasalso%C2%A0%20asked%20if%20he%20had%20covered%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20and%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20happened%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20They%20may%20call%20me%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20his%20investigative%20reports%20on%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20dealings%20and%20crony%20capitalism%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20officials%20asked%20him%20whether%20he%20had%20covered%20Delhi%20riots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20said%20no%20but%20then%20they%20asked%20me%20whether%20I%20reported%20on%20farmers%20protests.%20I%20said%20yes.%20There%20were%20many