0from%20people%20that%20left%20me%20shaken.%20People%20would%20shame%20me%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20you%20dress%3B%20you%20asked%20for%20it!%E2%80%99%20After%20a%20year%2C%20the%20scars%20started%20to%20fade%2C%20but%20the%20incident%20wrecked%20my%20self-confidence%20and%20left%20me%20very%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20was%20recovering%2C%20a%20family%20friend%20tried%20to%20assault%20her.%20When%20he%20did%20it%20again%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330948%2Fp-bindu-organic-farmer-tamil-nadu-innovation-msme-kvk-agriculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroke%20her%20silence.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Realising%20that%20there%20were%20many%20like%20her%20who%20must%20be%20afraid%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETaking%20strength%20from%20her%20father%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20stories%20I%20remember%20are%20of%20him%20being%20a%20great%20human%20being%20and%20a%20servant%20of%20the%20society.%20Even%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20like%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20started%20an%20NGO%20in%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20honour%20called%20Shaheed%20Ramashray%20Welfare%20Society%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20helping%20victims%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20and%20domestic%20violence%20get%20justice.%20The%20welfare%20society%20gives%20them%20free%20legal%20aid.%20Devanshi%20also%20gives%20them%20free%20counselling%20and%20accompanies%20victims%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGetting%20proper%20counselling%20and%20knowing%20the%20next%20steps%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20healing%20after%20abuse.%20The%20people%20who%20come%20to%20me%20are%20usually%20very%20scared%20and%20unsure%20of%20what%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%