sustainable%20fashion%20and%20creating%20high-end%2C%20experimental%20pieces%20using%20waste%20materials.%20Our%20designs%20prioritise%20functionality%20and%20longevity%20with%20diverse%20silhouettes.%20Our%20collection%20highlights%20innovative%20upcycling%20techniques%20with%20simple%20shapes%20and%20functional%20details%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Gouri%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%20this%20brand%2C%20we%20had%20this%20idea%20of%20working%20around%20sustainability.%20Coming%20from%20a%20design%20background%2C%20my%20initial%20thoughts%20were%20to%20create%20pieces%20that%20are%20so%20eclectic%20in%20nature%20and%20well%20thought%20out%20that%20people%20would%20be%20shocked%20to%20find%20out%20products%20like%20these%20are%20made%20out%20of%20waste.%20This%20was%20the%20design%20philosophy%20that%20more%20or%20less%20went%20into%20our%20products.%20For%20example%2C%20Noir%20Et%20Blanc%20features%20a%20monochromatic%20approach%2C%20while%20Gold%20Riddance%20uses%20bold%20gold%20tones.%20We%20showcase%20craftsmanship%20in%20our%20High-Braid%20all-upcycled%20leather%20line.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20accessories%20need%20to%20be%20very%20utilitarian%20and%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20just%20part%20of%20another%20fad.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20create%20accessories%20that%20would%20eventually%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%20once%20a%20seasonal%20trend%20has%20passed.%20They%20are%20durable%20in%20terms%20of%20material%2C%20utilitarian%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20functionality%2C%20and%20design-wise%2C%20they%20are%20archival%20so%20that%20they%20remain%20in%20your%20wardrobe%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoving%20ahead%2C%20however%2C%20they%20are%20expanding%20their%20product%20range%20to%20include%20jewellery%20crafted%20from%20scrap%20leather%20and%20metal%2C%20and%20have%20developed%20a%20new%20fabric%20made%20from%20waste%20threads.%20Emblematic%20of%20their%20new%20product%20range%20is%20their%20upcoming%20collection%20%E2%80%98Creation%20of%20Eve%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20reimagines%20the%20story%20of%20Eve%20(from%20Adam%20and%20Eve)%20through%20upcycled%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCould%20we%20show%20Eve%20in%20a%20more%20powerful%20light%20because%20she%20has%20been%20overlooked%20several%20times%20in%20history%3F%20We%20wanted%20to%20couple%20that%20idea%20with%20how%20people%20often%20overlook%20or%20forget%20waste%20as%20well%20and%20that%20is%20how%20we%20came%20up%20with%20a%20whole%20storyline%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20The%20technique%20employed%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20their%20Eve%20collection%20takes%20inspiration%20from%20the%20concept%20of%20Kintsugi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20to%20apply%20the%20same%20concept%20with%20scraps%20and%20join%20them%20with%20golden%20embroidery%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20zero%20wastage.%20We%20have%20created%20a%20whole%20fabric%20from%20waste%20threads%20coming%20out%20of%20shirts%20and%20T-shirts.%20As%20soon%20as%20you%20look%20at%20our%20collection%2C%20you%20can%20already%20see%20that%20there%20are%20smaller%20scraps%20in%20bits%20and%20pieces%20and%20a%20golden%20light%20that%20is%20gleaming%20from%20inside%20of%20it.%20That%20seemed%20like%20a%20great%20way%20to%20introduce%20the%20creation%20of%20Eve%20in%20her%20most%20powerful%20form%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Econock's%20mantra%20of%20sustainable%20fashion.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661-300x157.jpg%203