r%20boots.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20make%20shoes%20that%20are%20lightweight%20and%20can%20be%20worn%20without%20socks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Due%20to%20their%20natural%20makeup%2C%20these%20shoes%20won%E2%80%99t%20make%20your%20feet%20smell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20could%20also%20save%20unnecessary%20piling%20up%20of%20shoes%20in%20landfills%20as%20waste.%20We%20would%20also%20end%20up%20giving%20life%20to%20them%20by%20another%203-4%20years.%20Our%20father%20taught%20us%20the%20value%20of%20recycling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwrST7KS3lV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwrST7KS3lV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwrST7KS3lV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Divya%20(%40chaosinacoupe)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainable%20%26amp%3B%20sock-free%20shoes%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20research%20and%20development%20process%20of%20two%20years%2C%20the%20siblings%20found%20a%20sustainable%20alternative%20to%20manufacture%20environment-friendly%20shoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSugarcane%20is%20widely%20used%20in%20India.%20When%20we%20drink%20%3Cem%3Eganne%20ka%20juice%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sugarcane%20juice)%2C%20we%20see%20the%20slag%20left%20behind%20as%20residue.%20Being%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20field%2C%20I%20came%20across%20Brazilian%20resin%20supplier%20which%20innovated%20sugarcane%20EVA%20(ethylene%20vinyl%20acetate)%20copolymer%20derived%20from%20sugarcane%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Parth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20to%20utilise%20the%20innovative%20carbon-negative%20material%2C%20Parth%20collaborated%20with%20the%20company%20to%20use%20sugarcane%20EVA%20to%20make%20the%20shoes%E2%80%99%20outsoles%20soft%20and%20comfortable.%20Other%20than%20this%2C%20they%20incorporated%20renewable%20and%20recyclable%20materials%20like%20merino%20wool%20and%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20to%203D-knit%20the%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20shoes%20are%20made%20from%20recycled%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20Parth%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20make%20pallets%20from%20plastic%20bottles%20which%20are%20then%20melted%20into%20yarn.%20We%20then%20blend%20merino%20wool%20into%20it%20to%20make%20propitiatory%20threads.%20So%2C%20while%20the%20outsoles%20made%20from%20sugarcane%20EVA%20provide%20durability%20and%20flexibility%20to%20the%20shoe%2C%20yarns%20made%20from%20single-use%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20merino%20wool%20with%20its%20natural%20antibacterial%20properties%20provide%20comfort%20for%20long-day%20use.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interestingly%2C%20the%20duo%20recycles%2011%20plastic%20bottles%20to%20knit%20a%20pair%20of%20shoes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331143%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20duo%20recycles%2011%20plastic%20bottles%20to%20knit%20a%20pair%20of%20shoes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENeha%20Parekh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20using%20these%20shoes%20for%20almost%20four%20months%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20corporate%20job%2C%20I%20have%20to%20drive%20and%20stand%20for%20long%20hours.%20The%20shoes%20I%20would%20wear%20were%20not%20comfortable%20and%20made%20my%20feet%20sweaty.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20find%20some%20comfortable%20shoes%20or%20flats%20options%20which%20I%20could%20wear%20daily%20with%20minimal%20design.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20wore%20Reroute%20shoes%2C%20I%20did%20not%20feel%20like%20these%20shoes%20are%20made%20from%20plastic.%20They%20are%20very%20comfortable%20to%20wear.%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20feather%20on%20my%20skin.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriced%20at%20Rs%202%2C999%2C%20these%20shoes%20weigh%20180%20grams.%20Parth%20informs%20that%20between%2095%20and%20110%20grams%20of%20this%20comprise%20sugarcane%20residue.%20Interestingly%2C