%2F09%2FUntitled-design-7-1695812440-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-7-1695812440-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-7-1695812440-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331007%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20student-run%20wall%20magazines%20see%20contributions%20in%20the%20forms%20of%20writings%2C%20drawings%20and%20poems.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20initiative%20of%20magazines%20in%20schools%20and%20classrooms%20is%20building%20a%20writing%20culture%20among%20students.%20Writing%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20necessary%20practices%20every%20student%20should%20be%20familiar%20with.%20After%20getting%20inspiration%20from%20senior%20students%2C%20junior%20classes%20also%20released%20their%20wall%20magazines%20with%20the%20help%20of%20their%20teachers.%20In%20this%20initiative%2C%20students%20are%20not%20only%20building%20their%20writing%20skills%20but%20learning%20from%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20writing%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kamlesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENPS%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20work%20to%20encourage%20students%20to%20contextualise%20learning%20in%20their%20local%20surroundings.%20Kamlesh%20notes%20that%20the%20school%20identified%20that%20children%20are%20often%20oblivious%20to%20the%20things%20happening%20around%20them%20and%20that%20studying%20only%20within%20classroom%20settings%20without%20context%20or%20reference%20makes%20learning%20more%20abstract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20why%20they%20work%20on%20documenting%20stories%20of%20the%20people%20around%20them%2C%20focussing%20on%20their%20traditional%20art%20and%20craft%2C%20challenges%2C%20social%20issues%2C%20and%20customs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENPS%20collaborates%20with%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Archive%20of%20Rural%20India%20(PARI)%20to%20teach%20students%20reporting%2C%20data%20analysing%2C%20and%20ground%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20project%20is%20helping%20students%20to%20know%20more%20about%20the%20stories%20around%20them%20and%20learn%20from%20the%20ordinary%20people%20of%20day-to-day%20life.%20It%20helps%20senior%20students%20to%20get%20examples%20from%20their%20surroundings%20about%20what%20they%20are%20learning%20in%20the%20classroom.%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20is%20strengthening%20academic%20learning%20and%20helping%20to%20connect%20bookish%20concepts%20with%20the%20stories%20to%20get%20a%20better%20perspective%20of%20the%20particular%20topic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gurpreet%20Kaur%20(16)%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-8-1695812542.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Today%2C%20Kamlesh%20Atwal%20is%20fulfilling%20his%20dream%20of%20empowering%20rural%20students%20and%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20tools%20to%20gain%20confidence%20and%20secure%20a%20good%20career.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-8-1695812542.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-8-1695812542-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-8-1695812542-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-8-1695812542-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-8-1695812542-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331013%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20Kamlesh%20Atwal%20is%20f